{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_QC02_REG_015.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0x35,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x8,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "Anyway, it's been quite a while.<CR>Like, almost a year...?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Probably. It's been around that long since you came to visit me."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x9,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "And, so why are you going on this journey? Peddling medicine?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x6,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "How can I say this...?<CR>I'm looking for rare flowers."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0xa,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "Rare flowers? Are you gonna use them to synthesize medicine?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xc4,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "No. I don't know if you'll believe this or not, but..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xc5,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "I heard that they could be clues to finding Nio."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x122,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "Nio!?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x123,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "But...Nio was, you know...spirited away, and..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xcd,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "This person told me that Nio is still alive somewhere."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xce,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "If she is alive, I think I can do something to see her again."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xcf,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "It may sound impossible, but it's something I have to believe in."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x124,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "Hmm...so you decided to believe that person?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "Then, I'm in no position to fault you for it... Okay then, I'll help you."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x34,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "Hehe, thank you very much. I know this kind of story is hard to believe..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x37,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "But, just you saying that makes me happy."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3a,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "So, the clues that will help me find Nio are these glowing flowers..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "Glowing flowers? Being spirited away and flowers seem to have nothing to do with each other..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "I'm not sure about the details, but if I investigate the flowers, he said I can save Nio."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0xd4,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "msg_string": "But still, flowers...aren't my forte at all."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0xd6,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x14,
            "msg_string": "Oh, but...I think I know someone who might know about them."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x15,
            "msg_string": "Eh...really!?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x193,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x16,
            "msg_string": "Yup. There's a person who lives in Vierzeberg, a town to the north."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x8,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x17,
            "msg_string": "He likes rare things, and collects various items as a hobby."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x9,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x18,
            "msg_string": "As a patron of rare things, he might know something about rare flowers."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x19,
            "msg_string": "Umm, could you please introduce me to him...?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x195,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1a,
            "msg_string": "Yeah, sure. I was gonna go to Vierzeberg for some stuff after this anyways."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x10,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1b,
            "msg_string": "All right, if that's our plan, I'll hurry and get ready for the journey!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x193,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1c,
            "msg_string": "You're right. You'll probably need to pack some stuff."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x9,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1d,
            "msg_string": "Oh, that reminds me! Ayesha..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x9,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1e,
            "msg_string": "Didn't you bring too much stuff with you? You look more like you're moving away than going on a journey."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x34,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x1f,
            "msg_string": "Hahaha, and this is after I tried<CR>cutting back on the luggage.<CR>I've never been on a journey before..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0xf,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x20,
            "msg_string": "Why don't you leave the things you won't need here?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x36,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x21,
            "msg_string": "Huh? At your house...?<CR>But...are you sure?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x195,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x22,
            "msg_string": "Yeah. I have plenty of space anyways, so feel free to use it like your own house."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x23,
            "msg_string": "Thank you very much. Then, I'll take advantage of your kind offer."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x24,
            "msg_string": "I'll just put my cauldron down here for a moment."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x122,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x25,
            "msg_string": "What!? Ayesha, you were carrying that thing around?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x124,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x26,
            "msg_string": "I don't think you need that on your journey..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15a,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0x27,
            "msg_string": "Huh...? Really? But I start to get restless without my cauldron."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0xd0,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x28,
            "msg_string": "No, no, no! It's not like a pillow or anything. Normal people don't carry these around."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0xd2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x29,
            "msg_string": "Just leave it here...<CR>Pana must've had a tough time."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2a,
            "msg_string": "Okay, I'll do that! I'm happy I'll get to synthesize at your house."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x49,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x2b,
            "msg_string": "Haha, you sure do like to synthesize!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x2,
            "name_id": 0x2,
            "extra_id": 0x4b,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x2c,
            "msg_string": "Anyway, I'll be looking forward to spending time with you, Ayesha!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xffffffff,
            "name_id": 0xffffffff,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_string": "Regina can now join your party."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xffffffff,
            "name_id": 0xffffffff,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_string": "You can now use Regina's House."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xffffffff,
            "name_id": 0xffffffff,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_string": "You can now access Synthesis, Container, System Menu, and Journal from Regina's House."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xffffffff,
            "name_id": 0xffffffff,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_string": "From now on, more places where you can access Synthesis, Container, System Menu, and Journal may be added."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xffffffff,
            "name_id": 0xffffffff,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_string": "Use them well according to your purpose."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xffffffff,
            "name_id": 0xffffffff,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_string": "A character that can join your party has been added. Recruited members can go with Ayesha on her journey."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xffffffff,
            "name_id": 0xffffffff,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_string": "These friends can join you in battle, and help you in gathering. You can take a maximum of two friends."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xffffffff,
            "name_id": 0xffffffff,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_string": "Talk to characters in town and select \"Recruit\" to have them join your party. Select \"Part Ways\" to part company."
        }
    ]
}